                                        <div class="description">
                                            Please note that we are implementing the online payment transaction for the advance purchase reservations. In this process, we are sending a link to the email of the card holder and this allows them to purchase the amount directly from their credit card. This process is to avoid credit card purchase error from our side and to protect the guests from credit card fraud.
